query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('arkit',
'linq-to-entities',
'preg-replace',
'prototypejs',
'rendering',
'spark-dataframe',
'spring-batch',
'struts',
'visualization',
'word-vba');
